{"tid":2142112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【藍牙密佈變監控城市】 揭華為 Huawei監控裝置佈全香港  英美封殺港府獨撐","createTime":"2020-08-06T07:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:16:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2ee01c778a3bee4481f9b02526e2ce03b84eda","tid":2142112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#監控香港人 #華為 #壹週刊<br />\n<br />\n【藍牙密佈變監控城市】<br />\n揭華為 Huawei監控裝置佈全香港 <br />\n英美封殺港府獨撐<br />\n (壹週刊 Next)<br />\nAug 3, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4auU0cC8vH4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4auU0cC8vH4&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=16d7b4dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4auU0cC8vH4</a><br />\n<br />\n壹週刊 NEXT<br />\n557K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n中美5G科技戰，華為面對全球封殺，英國政府也宣佈明年起罷買華為5G設備，2027年前全面移除華為5G網絡設備。華為在外業務處處踫壁，但背靠祖國仍有生意之餘，香港也是其重要基地。港大多數電訊商均使用華為的通訊設備，李嘉誠的和記電訊（215）旗下3香港、李澤楷旗下香港電訊（6823）的CSL、1010與SUN Mobile品牌，還有中移動（941）的CMHK，市佔率估計已合共逾八成。不單在網絡設備有香港市場做後盾，連電訊設備，也有香港政府「包底」。本刊發現運輸署原來在全港主要幹道上，安裝了八十個華為生產電池的藍牙交通裝置，有IT界人士擔心，表面上測車流的裝置，實質上是監控香港人。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"115ff9ef2a6454dfe031ea363a670822be56fd70","tid":2142112,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"誠哥楷仔好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b580b4b6a4be0b8402692ae249ad388abceaadf5","tid":2142112,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59864f5859620f7a658b4af6463d324e930e20e5","tid":2142112,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa